snippet.title: KONAEちゃんのドキドキペンギン家族  - Konae-chan complete playthrough (Satellaview)
snippet.description: As opposed to my previous upload, this one has an entire playthrough for Konae-chan no DokiDoki Pengin Kazoku. In under 11 minutes. Yeah, the game's short.
